sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client App
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth & Rate Limiter
    participant Router as Model Router
    participant Serving as Model Serving
    participant Model as LLM (GPU)
    participant Logger as Logging & Metering

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions {model, messages, params}
    GW->>Auth: Validate API key + check quota
    Auth-->>GW: 401 Unauthorized (if invalid)
    Auth-->>GW: 429 Too Many Requests (if quota exceeded)
    Auth-->>GW: OK (valid, within quota)
    GW->>Router: Route to model cluster
    Router->>Serving: Forward request to serving replica
    Serving->>Serving: Tokenize prompt
    Serving->>Serving: KV cache lookup (prefix match)
    Serving->>Model: Forward pass (cached prefix skipped)
    Model-->>Serving: Logits for next token
    Serving->>Serving: Sample / decode next token
    Serving->>Model: Continue until EOS or max_tokens
    Model-->>Serving: Final token sequence
    Serving->>Serving: Detokenize output tokens
    Serving->>Logger: Record token counts + latency
    Logger-->>Serving: Ack
    Serving-->>GW: Response {id, choices, usage}
    GW-->>Client: HTTP 200 response with generated text
